<h1 class="how_to_use">How to use</h1>
<h3>
  When refering to gettopup.com (the easiest setup)
</h3>
<ol>
  <li>
    Include TopUp with the following:
    <div class="code">
      &lt;script type="text/javascript" src="http://gettopup.com/releases/latest/top_up.js"></script>
    </div>
    (for a specific version use <span class="code">/releases/1.3.2/top_up.js</span> for example)
  </li>
  <li>
    Add either the class <span class="code">top_up</span>, the attribute <span class="code">toptions</span> to your links or TopUp preset(s)
  </li>
  <li>
    Enjoy!
  </li>
</ol>
<h3>
  When hosting the source and images yourself
</h3>
<ol>
  <li>
    Download the <%= link_to "latest TopUp version", "http://gettopup.com/releases/packed/latest.tar.gz" %>
  </li>
  <li>
    Include TopUp with the following:
    <div class="code">
      &lt;script type="text/javascript" src="path/to/your/top_up.js"></script>
    </div>
  </li>
  <li>
    Add either the class <span class="code">top_up</span>, the attribute <span class="code">toptions</span> to your links or TopUp preset(s)
  </li>
  <li>
    Enjoy!
  </li>
</ol>
